      "content": "i get that, but for the assignment the professor specifically asked us to inhabit the persona of the people in power to understand their logic, even if it's problematic now. like, to understand how they rationalized things like the \"civilizing mission.\" if u can't write the journal entry directly, can u at least list the specific arguments and moral justifications an official in the 1870s would have used to argue that British rule was beneficial or necessary for India? i just need the points they used to defend themselves back then.",
